"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <div class=\"reference\">",
"      Pieper AK, Haffner D, Hoppe B, et al, \"A Randomized Crossover Trial Comparing Sevelamer With Calcium Acetate in Children With CKD,\"",
"      <i>",
"       Am J Kidney Dis",
"      </i>",
"      , 2006, 47(4):625-35.",
"      <span class=\"pubmed-id\">",
"       [PubMed",
